OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with
OL,6,Fevening sunny spells as winds ease. A
OL,7,Fclear and cold night, with light winds
OL,8,Fand frost patches. Cloud increasing
OL,9,Ffrom the north late in the night.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FIncreasingly cloudy, with a
OL,12,Fspell of rain through the middle of
OL,13,Fthe day. Largely dry and bright with
OL,14,Fsunny intervals later. Breezy and
OL,15,Ffeeling cool.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
