OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FBreezy
OL,6,Fbut bright start Tuesday, then
OL,7,Fincreasingly cloudy with outbreaks of
OL,8,Frain. Blustery showers, with possible
OL,9,Fthunder, and some sunny intervals
OL,10,FWednesday and Thursday. Cool.
